== 城市历史 ==
1644年，[[美国原住民|美国原住民]]将大都会岛出售给来自[[欧洲|欧洲]]的第一批定居者。<ref name="action148">{{cite journal | url=http://www.comics.org/issue/8417/ | title=Superman, Indian Chief | author=Hamilton, Edmund | journal=Action Comics | date=2950-07 | volume=1 | issue=148 | access-date=2018-03-27 | archive-date=2021-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224185856/https://www.comics.org/issue/8417/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> 这与[[纽约市|纽约市]]的历史相似，1626年，美国原住民将[[曼哈顿岛|曼哈顿岛]]出售给了来自[[荷兰|荷兰]]的定居者。<ref>Frederick M. Binder, David M. Reimers: All the Nations Under Heaven: An Ethnic and Racial History of New York City, p.4;(1996){{ISBN|0-231-07879-X}}</ref>

